document_data.Possessions:
In public, Tristan wore a heavy wool [[wikipedia:cloak|cloak]] over his leather [[trousers]] and dark leather boots.

In battle, he donned a suit of [[banded mail]] armor and wielded a longsword.

While on a mission to rescue [[Keren Donnell]], he serendipitously found the ''[[Sword of Cymrych Hugh]]'' hidden in a treasure chamber within a [[Firbolg]] stronghold.{{Cite digital book/Darkwalker on Moonshae|2568}} Keren recognized it for what it was and told Tristan that the weapon must be wielded by whoever finds it.{{Cite digital book/Darkwalker on Moonshae|2579}}
